attributes.title: The Anteallach Ale Co
attributes.description:
Created on February 28, 2010 by leo on Sourcemap.org:

Brewing moved to  the family croft at Camusnagaul, near Dundonnell, during March 2003.  Ales include An Teallach and Beinn Dearg.
